# SUB QEURY
------------

When we want data from one table with condition based on another table we will use **SUB QUERY** .

Q)Get the user from user table but only users whose city is hyderabad in address table

Ans) select * from users where user_id=
    (select user_id from address where city='Hyderabad')


# JOIN
--------
When we want data from two or more tables  we will use **JOIN** .

Q)Get the user from user table but only users whose city is hyderabad in address table

Ans) select u.user_id,u.user_name,u.user_email from users u inner join address a
     on u.user_id=a.user_id where a.city='Hyderabad'

Q)Get the user and address from both tables but only users whose city is hyderabad in address table

Ans) select u.user_id,u.user_name,u.user_email,a.address_id,
     a.city,a.country from users u inner join address a
     on u.user_id=a.user_id where a.city='Hyderabad'


     